title: DJ Josh  Vickers - MWS2 [320kbps/2007] Promo Techno Mix
description:
[b]DJ Josh Vickers -MindWaves Session 2 [/b]

An hour long non-stop mix featuring some of the best from the underground. The atmosphere starts of cold and hard, then gets more upbeat and warm when the frequencies start interjecting through the perfect mixing. The set list makes an almost conceptual dj-set as Josh Vickers mixes sounds in and out through the mix, with a skilful use of effects this mix is spot on for those messed up crazy nights!
 Dj Josh Vickers mixes with the attention of a minimalist but also with the attitude of a frantic raver! Powerful stuff! BPM varies from 130 - 140.
 
Its All Going Off!

 [i]Enjoy the mix, and pass it along :)
[/i]
